apt-notifier (1.0-2mlrepo1) mepis; urgency=low

  * Prefix apt-get upgrade command with LC_ALL=en_US
  * to make notifier work with non-english locales
  *
  * The apt-get command now uses the --trivial-only
  * option instead of the -s option. This eliminates
  * the "Inst" and "Conf" lines from the command's
  * output and speeds it up some.
  *
  * Added the -V option to the apt-get upgrade
  * command. The code to isolate the package names
  * is simpler with the -V option.
  *
  * Formatted the apt-notifier-check-Updates script
  * with line breaks "\" to hopefully make it
  * easier to understand.
  *
  * Removed disabled code sections
  *
  * Added synaptic as a dependency

